Umunyana Shanitah ni umunyarwandakazi witabiriye amarushanwa ya [[Nyampinga w'u Rwanda|nyampinga]] cyangwa umukobwa uhiga abandi

mubwiza no mubwenge mu [[Rwanda]] nubwo ataryegukanye ariko ntago byamubujuje kwegukana irushanwa ry'umukobwa

wahize abandi muri [[East African Christian College|east Africa]] bwambere mumateka iri rishanwa ryari ribaye. rikabera mugihugu cyabaturanyi cya [[Tanzaniya]]<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/entertainment/what-you-need-know-about-miss-east-africa-2021</ref>

== Miss Umunyana Shsnitah ==
umunyana shanitah ni umukowa wari uhagarariye u Rwanda mu irushanwa rya [[East African Christian College|miss east Africa]] ryaberaga muri [[Tanzaniya]] akaba ari nawe<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/112908/umunyana-shanitah-yegukanye-ikamba-rya-miss-east-africa-2021-amafoto-112908.html</ref> 

wegukanye [[Ikambere (ikinyamakuru)|ikamba]] rya [[Nyampinga w'u Rwanda|Miss Suprenational]] 2019 mu gihugu cye cyu Rwanda sibyo gusa kuko yagiye yitabira amarushanwa yubwiza menshi 

atandukaanye mu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] ndetse no Hanze yarwo kugeza nubwo ariwe watwaye ikamba rya [[East African Christian College|Miss East Africa]] 2021 bwambere ubwo yahatanaga 

nabandi bakobwa nabo bahagarariye ibihugu byabo.<ref>https://taarifa.rw/rwandan-crowned-miss-east-africa-2021/</ref>

== Akamaro (empowement) ==
ubusanzwe [[Nyampinga w'u Rwanda|irushanwa rya Nyampinga]] ni urushanwa ritwabwa nu mukobwa uhiga abandi mu bwiza [[Umuco nyarwanda|mu mico]] no mumyitwarire<ref>https://taarifa.rw/rwandan-crowned-miss-east-africa-2021/</ref>

bavuga ko kandi ari irushanwa ritera abana babakobwa ikizere kwisobanukirwa ndetse no gutinyuka bakanagaragaza imishinga yabo

itandukanye maze igaterwa inkunga nababifite munshingano ni irushanwa kandi ritinyura abana babakobwa mukuvuga ndetse no gukora

ndetse no kongerera ubushobozi abagore binyuze binyuze mubuhanga bwimibereho ndetse no kwihangira imirimo

